      <title>禁售协议到期后 Americanas 股价下跌 50%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/americanas-shares-sink-50-as-lock-up-agreement-ends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西零售商 Americanas SA 因大规模会计欺诈而陷入破产保护，在其债务重组后大多数债权人的禁售期结束后，其股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/americanas-shares-sink-50-as-lock-up-agreement-ends</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
