    <item>
      <title>奥默斯基金受益于信贷和美元的推动，上半年回报率为 4.4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/omers-gets-tailwind-from-credit-and-us-dollar-returns-4-4-in-first-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受股票、私人信贷和美元敞口的推动，安大略省市政雇员退休系统 (Ontario Municipal Employees Retirement System) 上半年回报率为 4.4%。]]></description>
